OL,3,CScott Mills was BBC's highest earner
OL,4,Cuntil he was sacked
OL,6,FFormer BBC Radio 2 presenter Scott
OL,7,FMills was the corporation's highest
OL,8,Fearner until he was sacked in March
OL,9,Fafter it emerged that he had been
OL,10,Finvestigated for historical sexual
OL,11,Foffences, figures reveal.
OL,13,FThe 53-year-old earned between
OL,14,F#745,000 and #749,999 for the year
OL,15,Fending in March 2026, according to the
OL,16,FBBC's Annual Report, for work on the
OL,17,FBBC Radio 2 Breakfast Show, which he
OL,18,Ftook over from Zoe Ball in January
OL,19,F2025; Pop: Top 10 shows and various
OL,20,Fother engagements across public
OL,21,Fservice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
