OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784112473
OL,3,CScott Mills was BBC's highest earner
OL,4,Cuntil he was sacked
OL,6,FMills was sacked by the BBC shortly
OL,7,Fbefore it emerged that the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police had launched an
OL,9,Finvestigation into him in 2016 over
OL,10,Fallegations of serious sexual offences
OL,11,Finvolving a boy aged under 16 between
OL,12,F1997 and 2000.
OL,14,FHe was sacked after the corporation
OL,15,Fsaid it had received "new information"
OL,16,Fregarding the case.
OL,18,FThe police investigation was closed in
OL,19,F2019 after prosecutors decided there
OL,20,Fwas insufficient evidence to bring
OL,21,Fcharges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
