FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784112473
OL,3,CScott Mills was BBC's highest earner
OL,4,Cuntil he was sacked
OL,6,FMills confirmed at the time: "An
OL,7,Fallegation was made against me in 2016
OL,8,Fof a historic sexual offence which was
OL,9,Fthe subject of a police investigation
OL,10,Fin which I fully co-operated and
OL,11,Fresponded to in 2018.
OL,13,F"As the police have stated, a file of
OL,14,Fevidence was submitted to the Crown
OL,15,FProsecution Service, which determined
OL,16,Fthat the evidential threshold had not
OL,17,Fbeen met to bring charges."
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
