OL,3,CScott Mills was BBC's highest earner
OL,4,Cuntil he was sacked
OL,6,FThe Southampton-born presenter earned
OL,7,Fbetween #355,000 and #359,999 in last
OL,8,Fyear's report, when he was the joint
OL,9,F11th highest earner alongside Naga
OL,10,FMunchetty.
OL,12,FFormer England footballer Gary
OL,13,FLineker, once the BBC's highest-paid
OL,14,Fstar, earned between #325,000 and
OL,15,F#329,999 for the year to March 2026,
OL,16,Fplacing him 15th in the most recent
OL,17,Flist, having left the BBC in May last
OL,18,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
