OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784112473
OL,3,CScott Mills was BBC's highest earner
OL,4,Cuntil he was sacked
OL,6,FHe had a salary between # 1,350,000
OL,7,Fand #1,354,999 in the last annual
OL,8,Freport.
OL,10,FLineker's 2025/2026 earnings came from
OL,11,Fhis work on the Premier League
OL,12,Fhighlights show Match Of The Day and
OL,13,Fother football coverage.
OL,15,FLineker was not the only high earner
OL,16,Fto depart the BBC, as Ball no longer
OL,17,Ffeatures on the list.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
