OL,3,CScott Mills was BBC's highest earner
OL,4,Cuntil he was sacked
OL,6,FBall was second on last year's highest-
OL,7,Fpaid list, and will now present an
OL,8,Fafternoon show on Greatest Hits Radio
OL,9,Ffrom September.
OL,11,FBBC Match Of The Day football pundit
OL,12,Fand former Newcastle United striker
OL,13,FAlan Shearer saw his pay decrease from
OL,14,Fbetween #440,000 and #444,999 last
OL,15,Fyear, to between #390,000 and
OL,16,F#394,999, making him sixth on the list.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
