OL,3,CScott Mills was BBC's highest earner
OL,4,Cuntil he was sacked
OL,6,FBBC political journalist Laura
OL,7,FKuenssberg was the highest-paid female
OL,8,Fstaff member with a salary of between
OL,9,F#405,000 and #409,999 in the latest
OL,10,Freport.
OL,12,FThe second-highest-paid staff member
OL,13,Fwas BBC Radio 1 DJ Greg James, who
OL,14,Fearned between #440,000 and #444,999,
OL,15,Fand the third-highest-paid was
OL,16,FNorthern Irish radio presenter Stephen
OL,17,FNolan, with a salary of between
OL,18,F#425,000 and #429,999.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
