OL,3,CScott Mills was BBC's highest earner
OL,4,Cuntil he was sacked
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FKuenssberg was fourth on the list,
OL,12,Fjoint with Radio 2 presenter Vernon
OL,13,FKay.
OL,15,FSeventh on the list was journalist
OL,16,FJustin Webb with a salary between
OL,17,F#375,000 and #379,999, and eighth was
OL,18,FMunchetty with a salary of between
OL,19,F#360,000 and #364,999.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
