OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784112473
OL,3,CScott Mills was BBC's highest earner
OL,4,Cuntil he was sacked
OL,6,FThe top 10 was rounded off with
OL,7,FQuestion Time presenter Fiona Bruce,
OL,8,Fwith a salary ranging between #345,000
OL,9,Fand #349,999, placing her ninth; and
OL,10,Fjournalist Sophie Raworth in 10th with
OL,11,Fa salary of between #340,000 and
OL,12,F#344,999.
OL,14,FFour women featured in this year's top
OL,15,F10, up from three last year.
OL,17,FThe list does not include people who
OL,18,Fare paid through independent
OL,19,Fproduction companies or the BBC's
OL,20,Fcommercial arm, BBC Studios.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
